{"tid":2003883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[勞資糾紛，手足唔割]港男參加反送中來台避難 竟涉檢屍性侵女戰友","createTime":"2020-05-06T06:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T03:30:14.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ef0bbdb115e1df340325d49cadea4ac89ae65e75","tid":2003883,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:00:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200506%2FFDHNOA65HB7MFFCY2SEFSXHUDQ%2F&amp;d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&amp;h=51a53dcf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fr.lihkg.com%2Flink%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ftw.appledaily.com%252Flocal%252F20200506%252FFDHNOA65HB7MFFCY2SEFSXHUDQ%252F%26d%3DLQBsT8b49a%252FdXTDbQfnWX34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%253D%26h%3D51a53dcf&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KROgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=63442973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200506%2FFDHNOA65HB7MFFCY2SEFSXHUDQ%2F&amp;d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&amp;h=51a53dcf</a><br />\n<br />\n香港男子馬靖翔去年在香港參加反送中後，因為怕中共政權迫害，去年底來台灣讀書避難，沒想到遭同為反送中的同鄉女子，指控在一場餐敍後，將酒醉意識不清的她帶到旅館性侵，檢警獲報後在前天(4日)將他拘提到案，訊問後諭令1萬元交保，並限制出境、出海及住居。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，這件性侵疑雲發生在今年3、4月間，在台灣讀書的香港男子馬靖翔，與一同參加過反送中的女性友人在台北西門町聚餐，他鄉遇故知，2人在這次餐敍聊得相當愉快，也喝了一點酒，用餐後為了安全起見，2人在附近的一家旅館休息過夜。<br />\n<br />\n不料事隔1個多月後，女子向警方報案，指控當天與馬靖翔用餐後，因為喝了不少，在酒醉意識不清的情況下，被對方撿屍性侵，她沒想到昔日的戰友竟然對她做這種事，害她痛不欲生，她想了又想，決定站出來提告，揭發對方的惡行。<br />\n<br />\n對於被控撿屍性侵，馬靖翔否認犯罪，據悉，他到案後表示，當天他確實與告訴人在用餐後發生性關係，但否認違背對方的意願，辯稱當天女子並無意識不清，是她主動投懷送抱，2人自然發生關係，絕對沒有違背對方的意願。<br />\n<br />\n他還表示，因為他在香港從事反送中的社會運動，有人一直要搞他，千方百計的找他麻煩，他是被冤枉的，請檢察官一定要明察，還他清白。<br />\n<br />\n檢察官訊問後，認為尚有事證待釐清，因此以涉犯趁機性交罪諭令1萬元交保，同時限制出境、出海及住居。馬靖翔在獲保後，自己拿出錢來辦保，並由萬華分局警員陪同離開北檢。"},{"pid":"b10511b80e9b3511a5aeb89e90ad915461b936ce","tid":2003883,"uid":133680,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:01:30.000Z","msg":"一個月先報警，唔好玩啦，唔好一年後報警?想用中國式陰道抹黑我地手足，唔割!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2845bc6079ae54fd15b0b6e5d7f968ccaf5613","tid":2003883,"uid":311611,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:01:59.000Z","msg":"淫棍不用回來了"},{"pid":"e0b79ffdc91e1286a003ae269267f1c33f1244bf","tid":2003883,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:04:37.000Z","msg":"台灣好多女屈男"},{"pid":"b170843d80f7665f57eabc9095c3bd240d633204","tid":2003883,"uid":8014,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:06:11.000Z","msg":"香港抗爭者個朵就係比呢啲人玩臭晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e4ea7b7e95ea22cadbf6657803edb4554710e1","tid":2003883,"uid":63117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:09:55.000Z","msg":"害群之馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15f41fcebf98b09ef89df14028fad1c9f46265a","tid":2003883,"uid":182610,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ef0bbdb115e1df340325d49cadea4ac89ae65e75","tid":2003883,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:00:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200506%2FFDHNOA65HB7MFFCY2SEFSXHUDQ%2F&amp;d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&amp;h=51a53dcf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fr.lihkg.com%2Flink%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ftw.appledaily.com%252Flocal%252F20200506%252FFDHNOA65HB7MFFCY2SEFSXHUDQ%252F%26d%3DLQBsT8b49a%252FdXTDbQfnWX34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%253D%26h%3D51a53dcf&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KROgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=63442973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200506%2FFDHNOA65HB7MFFCY2SEFSXHUDQ%2F&amp;d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&